TextEng: I understand, Fenthick. These are troubled times.
I am honored to serve Neverwinter, Fenthick.
I'll only serve if I am well paid, Fenthick.
It be honor for me serve Neverwinter.
Me only serve if me get gold.
He has no right to speak about me like that!
Text: 그가 나를 그렇게 말할 권리는 없어!

TextEng: Desther had better watch his mouth or he might lose some teeth!
Text: 데스터는 말조심하는 게 좋을 겁니다, 안 그러면 이빨 몇 개 잃을지도 몰라요!

TextEng: That okay. Me understand. This be tough times.
Text: 괜찮아. 나 이해. 지금 힘든 때.

TextEng: Him should not speak at me like that!
Text: 걘 내게 그렇게 말하면 안 돼!

TextEng: Desther better watch him mouth or me smash him face!
Text: 데스터 입 조심해. 안 그러면 나 얼굴 박살낸다!

TextEng: Rumors?
I wish to ask you some questions, Fenthick.
Where can I find Lady Aribeth?
Text: 아리베스 경은 어디에서 뵐 수 있죠?

TextEng: I thought you might be interested in this note.
Text: 이 쪽지를 보시는 게 좋을 것 같습니다.

TextEng: I'll be going now.
I will go to Aribeth at once!
I want to ask you some questions.
I guess I better go talk to Aribeth if I want any kind of reward from all this.
Text: 보상을 받으려면 아리베스 경과 이야기하러 가야겠군요.

TextEng: Me go Aribeth right now!
Me got questions me want ask.
Me better go talk at Aribeth if me want get gold for all this.
Text: 나 금화 받으려면 아리베스랑 얘기하러 가야 해.

TextEng: Me want ask you some stuff.
Text: 나 너한테 물을 것 좀 있어.

TextEng: Where me find Aribeth?
Me think you want look at this note.
Text: 나 너 이 쪽지 보고 싶을 것 같아.

TextEng: Me go now.
What do you know about the attack on the Academy?
Text: 사관학교가 습격당한 일에 대해 무엇을 알려 주실 수 있습니까?

TextEng: Tell me about the plague.
Text: 울부짖는 죽음 역병에 대해 말씀해 주세요.

TextEng: What do you know about a cure for the plague?
Text: 울부짖는 죽음 역병 치료법에 대해 아시는 게 있습니까?

TextEng: Tell me about Aribeth.
What do you know about Desther?
What you know 'bout attack at Academy?
You tell 'bout plague.
You know stuff 'bout plague cure?
You tell 'bout Aribeth?
What is your role in all this, Fenthick?
Text: 펜딕, 이 일에서 당신의 역할은 무엇입니까?

TextEng: What you do here, Fenthick?
What you know 'bout Desther?
This is no trick!
Why would I do such a thing?
This not be trick!
Why me want trick you?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Fenthick should follow every lead if he wants to find out who's behind this.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 범인을 찾으려면 펜딕은 가능한 모든 실마리를 따라가야 합니다.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> What's the matter, Desther? Do you have something to hide?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 왜 그러죠, 데스터? 뭔가 숨기는 겁니까?

TextEng: It is an honor to serve Neverwinter, Fenthick.
Is there some type of reward for bringing this to your attention?
Me just happy to help.
You gonna give me gold for note now?
Text: 이 쪽지 줬으니 금화 줄 거야?

TextEng: Thank you, Fenthick. You are very generous.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> This note was not easy to obtain, Fenthick. Not easy at all.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 이 쪽지를 구하는 일은 정말 쉽지 않았습니다, 펜딕.

TextEng: You better dig a little deeper or you won't live long enough to die from the plague!
Text: 좀 더 내놓는 게 좋을걸요, 안 그러면 역병으로 죽기도 전에 내가 먼저 죽여버릴 테니!

TextEng: Thanks. You nice man.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me work hard for note. Real hard.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 이 쪽지 구하려고 고생했어. 진짜 고생.

TextEng: You give more gold or me kill you faster than plague!
Text: 금화 더 줘. 아니면 역병보다 먼저 내가 널 죽여!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Say, Desther - you Helmites are kind of like a cult, aren't you?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 그런데 데스터, 당신들 헬름 신자들-일종의 사교도 같은 거 아닌가요?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> A cult could have both the organization and the determination to be behind this.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 이런 일을 저지를 조직력과 집요함은 사교도가 갖추기 쉽죠.

TextEng: The note is real, Desther!
Why would I make a fake note about a cult in Neverwinter?
Text: 내가 왜 네버윈터의 사교도에 관한 가짜 쪽지를 만들겠어?

TextEng: Note be real!
Why me want make fake note 'bout cult?
Text: 나 왜 사교도 가짜 쪽지 만들겠어?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> You knew the creatures were at the Academy, didn't you Desther?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 그 생명체들이 사관학교에 있었다는 걸 알고 있었죠, 데스터?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> The attackers knew enough to go straight to where the creatures were being held.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 습격자들은 생명체들이 보관된 장소를 정확히 알고 곧장 들이닥쳤습니다.

TextEng: This information is still worth investigating.
Text: 그래도 이 정보는 조사할 가치가 있습니다.

TextEng: Me think we still got look into this.
Text: 나 그래도 이거 조사해야 한다고 봐.

TextEng: Aren't you afraid of catching the plague yourself?
You not be afraid of get sick, too?
It like me drafted or something. Why me gotta care about this?
Text: 나 억지로 끌려온 것 같아. 왜 내가 이거 신경 써야 해?

TextEng: It seems I have been drafted into this. Why should I care about this?
Text: 억지로 끌려든 것 같은데요. 왜 제가 이 일을 신경 써야 하죠?
